OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Online shopping giant Amazon has said  
OL,6, it is "proud" of its contribution to   
OL,7, the UK economy, as it reveals its      
OL,8, latest financial results.              
OL,10,FThe firm paid #492m in taxes on sales  
OL,11,Fwhich rose 50% to #20.63bn, amid a     
OL,12,FCovid-driven surge in demand.          
OL,14,FAmazon and other tech firms, which pay 
OL,15,Ftax on profits not sales, have faced   
OL,16,Fscrutiny over the level of their tax   
OL,17,Fbills in the UK.                       
OL,19,FBut Amazon said it had invested #32bn  
OL,20,Fin UK infrastructure since 2010.       
